  "remarks": "\nFirst Deputy-Chairman of the Foreign Affairs Committee of the Federation Council of the Russian Federation.  On 1 March 2014 Dzhabarov, on behalf of the Foreign Affairs Committee of the Federation Council, publicly supported in the Federation Council the deployment of Russian forces in Ukraine.  \n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
